item.title: CVE-2019-0072|2024-08-04T17:37:07.541Z -- juniper%20networks -- sbr%20carrier
item.description: An Unprotected Storage of Credentials vulnerability in the identity and access management certificate generation procedure allows a local attacker to gain access to confidential information. This issue affects: Juniper Networks SBR Carrier: 8.4.1 versions prior to 8.4.1R13; 8.5.0 versions prior to 8.5.0R4.
